metadata.name: Le Fruit #0001
metadata.description: Le Fruit is a free mint project that focusing on its community, giving rarity based utility and building a web3 brand. Not a CC0, no bots, no super-expectations nor unthinkable promises are made. It consists of 5,000 dynamic NFTs which stored in the Ethereum blockchain, from the fruitionverse, from the web3 people, to the web3 people. Paid minters, engagers and builders of Le Fruit brand will eventually enjoy the highest priority of rewards as a token of appreciation for maintaining the prosperity of the Fruitionverse.
